                                <h4 class="text-white"><div class="bubble action"><i class="fa fa-bullhorn"></i></div> Empowering Action</h4>
                                <p class="mb-0 text-white-50">Climate-initatives should be powered by democratic technology and trustworthy data. Our map visualizes pollution hotspots based on data from several sources like <a href="https://www.nasa.gov/" target="_blank">NASA</a>, <a href="http://www.esa.int/" target="_blank">ESA</a>, <a href="https://www.wri.org/" target="_blank">WRI</a>, and <a href="https://www.eea.europa.eu/" target="_blank">EEA</a>. <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/decarbnow" target="_blank">#decarbnow</a> empowers both climate-science and climate-action in one interactive map. </p>
